projects.name: Character Customization application
projects.description: Create an avatar app from a free library of illustrations that allow users to choose from different options like face, hair, clothes.... using HTML, CSS and React.

projects.name: Movie application
projects.description: Developed a movie app using React, integrated the app with third-party APIs to fetch movie data, including details, ratings, and reviews. Implemented search and filtering functionalities to allow users to discover movies based on various genres.

projects.name: Music generation
projects.description: Implemented a deep learning model using Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks to generate classical music compositions in MIDI format. Constructed and trained the neural network using TensorFlow and Keras. The project successfully generated music using a dataset comprising 20 to 100 MIDI files.

projects.name: Potholes Database Management
projects.description: Designed and implemented a new database for the Austin Department of Public Works' Pothole Tracking and Repair System (PTRS) on an AWS PostgreSQL instance. Developed a web-based system for interactive data entry and queries to log and manage pothole reports. Created a schema to store detailed information on pothole locations, sizes, repair priorities, work orders, and associated property damage records.
